      },
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model benchmarked against FDA PIV dataset; normalized RMS velocity error 9.3% in impeller passage. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used with coefficients from Heuser & Opitz (1980) shear validation. Model form adequacy confirmed at required level 4."
